## Classes

### Class 35

Brand management services; business reputation management and improvement services; business consultancy; business management consultancy; consultancy relating to search engine optimization; statistical analysis and reporting services for business purposes.

### Class 42

Artificial intelligence as a service [AIaaS]; platform as a service [PaaS]; software as a service [SaaS]; providing online non-downloadable computer software; application service provider [ASP] services; cloud computing services; computer software design; computer system design; computer security consultancy; consultancy and information services relating to information technology; web scraping services; web crawling services.

### Class 45

Consultancy services relating to security; domain name monitoring services.

